707489f-a.title: Brooklyn: Ave. Z - 17th St. E.
707489f-a.text:
Ave. 2 at the N.E. corner of East 17th Street. Automobiles are parked
on the Long Island Railroad right of way which once extended along the
front of homes in this view.
July 9, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
